'''Snails''' were gastropods, noted for their low speed.<ref>{{HM|FR}}, "[[A Short Cut to Mushrooms]]"</ref> There were exceptionally large ones around [[Lonely Mountain|Erebor]], one of which fell victim to a [[thrushes|thrush]], as observed by [[Bilbo Baggins|Bilbo]] and [[Balin]].<ref>{{HM|H}}, "[[On the Doorstep]]"</ref> Most of them did not survive the onset of [[Smaug]].<ref>{{HM|H}}, "[[The Gathering of the Clouds]]"</ref>

